    body: 'The principles of dog training, such as reinforcement and positive reinforcement schedules, are backed by solid data and research. For owners, this means applying proven methods that foster trust and cooperation with your dog. Knowing how to reward good behaviour at the right time helps build a strong, positive bond between you and your pet.',
